high_descs: go straight and face the objects on the green dresser cabinets
pick up the middle tissue box from the top of the green cabinets
turn around and face the toilet
place the box of tissues on the top of the toilet tank, in front of the candle
return to the green cabinets
pick up the tissue box on the far left
go back to the toilet
place the tissue box vertically oriented on top of the toilet tank behind the first tissue box
anns.task_desc: Move two tissue boxes from the green cabinet counter top to the toilet

high_descs: Walk up to the right side of the teal dresser.
Pick up the middle box of tissues off of the dresser.
Walk over to the toilet behind you.
Put the box of tissues on the closest end of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk back over to the dresser.
Pick up the leftmost box of tissues off of the dresser.
Walk back over to the toilet behind you.
Put the box of tissues onto the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two boxes of tissues to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Proceed to counter in front of tissue boxes.
Pick up middle tissue box from counter.
Turn around, go to counter toilet.
Place tissue box on back of toilet, in front of candle stick.
Turn around, proceed to counter.
Pick up tissue box from counter, directly to left of pump dispenser.
Turn around, proceed to toilet.
Place tissue box on back of toilet, on its side, to the right of the candle.
anns.task_desc: Move two boxes of tissue from counter to back of toilet.
